Correct
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18 It looks as if A and B were matbogi, but actually there is a small difference between both points. When Black plays at 1, White needs to cut at 2 first, so Black can occupy the second vital point at 3 too.
\par
\par }
