Wrong
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par The hane at 1 doesn't work here because White will throw in at 2 and then make two eyes with the atari at 4. Due to chokchoksu Black can't connect at A, or White would capture at B.
\par }
